snippet: Lleyton Hewitt won a title for the first time since 2010 with an upset 6-1, 4-6, 6-3 win at the Brisbane International over Roger Federer, his longest-standing rival on tour....

headline.print_headline: Hewitt Upsets Federer to Win Brisbane Title
headline.main: Hewitt Upsets Federer to Win Brisbane Title

lead_paragraph: Lleyton Hewitt won a title for the first time since 2010 with an upset 6-1, 4-6, 6-3 win at the Brisbane International over Roger Federer, his longest-standing rival on tour.
